N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 609.6 - Other conditions and standards

State Regulations

If any provisions or requirements in this Subchapter of
department regulations are rendered inoperative, ineffective or inconsistent as
the result of any legislative, judicial or superseding administrative revisions
or mandates, any interim procedures, directions or interpretations so labelled
or described will take precedence over the described
regulations. Notes
